arChildNodes.szComment:
EXT. KED-BARDU - PIGSTY
The player picks up a bucket of water and tosses it on Lorath. Lorath starts and sputters before groggily sitting up. 
The initial jolt has sent a spike of pain into his head. He places both hands against his head and groans.
The player looks over at the ground and then, back to Lorath, ignoring his request.
gestures around in the pause between "this" and "patch"
Lorath does not speak right away. He takes slow deliberate breaths. It’s hard to tell if it’s to calm his head or to think.
Lorath shakes his head and then winces again.
Lorath pauses again, wiping at his face, rubbing his hands together to stop the shaking. He is struggling with what comes next.
He is starting to get to his feet slowly, wiping his hands on his robes.
He jerks his hand, pointing away from himself. Not looking at the player.
